etmaster.co.uk/86tvs-tickets/artist/5418565?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wwEzBLW-RxyPWNIXqSXj8x-BUkCxDbRucSNiXA0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里查找剩余的门票</a>。</p><p>怀特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/86tvs-discuss-the-perfect-heartbreak-of-the-maccabees-never-headlining-reading-leeds-3489962">在 2023 年接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>谈到了马卡比乐队从未成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024">雷丁和利兹的</a>头条新闻的“完美的心碎”。 “我们已经非常接近它了，伙计，”雨果补充道。 “我们 [2016 年] 成为了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/various-artists-397-1191400">Latitude</a>的头条新闻，这是我们迈向这件事的第一步。阅读总是在清单上。”</p><p>自 The Maccabees 解散以来，Orlando Weeks 制作了三张个人唱片： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/orlando-weeks-a-quickening-album-review-2686129">《A Quickening》</a> （2020 年）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/orlando-weeks-hop-up-review-3137853#:~:text=This%20is%20an%20album%20about,dreary%20day%2Dto%2Dday.">《Hop Up》</a> （2022 年）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-orlando-weeks-simmering-new-single-dig-featuring-wet-legs-rhian-teasdale-3751890">《Loja》</a> （2024 年）。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-maccabees-announce-huge-reunion-show-for-all-point-east-2025-buy-tickets-3806881">The Maccabees 宣布 2025 年 All Point East 大型重聚演出的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
